# Implementation Plan - Portfolio Website Clone

## Goal Description
Clone the portfolio website `https://vanshmadaan-dev.netlify.app/` ("same to same") using a modern tech stack.
The target site is a single-page React application using Tailwind CSS.
We will replicate the visual design, animations, and content structure.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> Since the visual assets (images, logos) cannot be scraped directly due to tool limitations, we will use placeholders or generic developer-themed assets initially.
> **Please provide any specific images (profile picture, project screenshots) you want to include.**

## Proposed Changes

### Tech Stack
- **Framework**: React (Vite)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **Fonts**: Fredoka (Headings/Accents), Poppins (Body)
- **Icons**: React Icons (Fa, Fi, Si sets)

